parameters: Beauty is how you feel inside, and it reflects in your eyes. It is not something physical.
Art is the imposing of a pattern on experience, and our aesthetic enjoyment is recognition of the pattern.
Girls have always been told that their value is tied to their appearance; their accomplishments are always magnified if they're pretty and diminished if they're not.
